# FileFree Brand Guide

## Brand Name

- **Product name**: FileFree (one word, camelCase capital F's)
- **Domain**: filefree.tax
- **Never**: File Free, Filefree, FILE FREE, File-Free, FileFree Tax

## Logo Assets

All assets in `web/public/brand/`:

| Asset | File | Usage |
|-------|------|-------|
| Wordmark (dark bg) | `filefree-wordmark-dark.png` | Hero sections, marketing, presentations |
| FF Monogram | `filefree-monogram.png` | App icon, social avatars, favicon source |
| Social Avatar | `filefree-avatar.png` | TikTok, Instagram, X, YouTube profile pictures |
| OG Image | `filefree-og.png` | Social sharing previews (1200x630) |
| Favicon | `favicon.svg` | Browser tab icon |

### Logo Rules

- Minimum clear space: half the height of the logo on all sides
- Never rotate, skew, add shadows, or place on busy backgrounds
- On dark backgrounds: use the wordmark as-is (white + gradient)
- On light backgrounds: use solid indigo (#4F46E5) for the full wordmark
- Never use the gradient on light backgrounds — it loses contrast

